iki/Portrait_of_Margaret_van_Eyck\" title=\"Portrait of Margaret van Eyck\">Portrait of Margaret van Eyck</a></i> (1439)</li></ul>\n</div></td><td class=\"navbox-image\" rowspan=\"8\" style=\"width:1px;padding:0px 0px 0px 2px\"><div><a href=\"/wiki/File:Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Portrait of a Man by Jan van Eyck-small.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8b/Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg/140px-Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg\" width=\"140\" height=\"192\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8b/Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg/210px-Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8b/Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg/280px-Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"2356\" data-file-height=\"3233\" /></a></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%;background: #f3e9d4\">Single religious<br />works</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;background: #fefcf6\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Annunciation_(van_Eyck,_Madrid)\" title=\"Annunciation (van Eyck, Madrid)\">Annunciation, Madrid</a></i>  (c. 1432\u201334)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Saint_Francis_Receiving_the_Stigmata_(van_Eyck)\" title=\"Saint Francis Receiving the Stigmata (van Eyck)\">St. Francis Receiving the Stigmata</a></i> (c. 1432\u201340)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Annunciation_(van_Eyck,_Washington)\" title=\"Annunciation (van Eyck, Washington)\">Annunciation, Washington</a></i> (c. 1434\u201336)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Madonna_of_Chancellor_Rolin\" title=\"Madonna of Chancellor Rolin\">Madonna of Chancellor Rolin</a></i> (1435)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Lucca_Madonna\" title=\"Lucca Madonna\">Lucca Madonna</a></i> (143